translation.Name: Buak_Note_07
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_0: The people in the suits keep coming back each month to drop off more cars, sometimes just one, sometimes upwards of ten. It's like they are some dealership scrapping failed models, but that can’t be right… Some of these cars date back to the 80’s, my dad owned one of the models back in the day… Whatever is going on I’m not crazy enough to confront them.
